item.title: CVE-2023-46650|2024-09-17T14:05:54.759Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20github%20plugin
item.description: Jenkins GitHub Plugin 1.37.3 and earlier does not escape the GitHub project URL on the build page when showing changes, resulting in a stored cross-site scripting (XSS) vulnerability exploitable by attackers with Item/Configure permission.
